title: Slow cooker chicken stew
ingredients: ['4 large skinless chicken breast fillets, cut into cubes', '10 medium red potatoes, quartered', '225g baby carrots', '120g chopped celery', '5 (295g) tins condensed cream of chicken soup', '6 cubes chicken stock', '2 teaspoons garlic salt', '1 teaspoon celery salt', '1 tablespoon ground black pepper', '450g frozen mixed vegetables']
